# Vanto Coach - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values

# ============================================
# AI PROCESSING (OPTIONAL)
# ============================================
# OpenAI API key for enhanced AI-powered transcript processing
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# If not provided, the app will use local fallback processing
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-api-key-here

# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# - The OpenAI integration is optional
# - Without an API key, the app uses intelligent local processing
# - With an API key, you get:
#   - GPT-4o-mini powered transcript cleaning
#   - More accurate mood detection
#   - Better action item extraction
#   - Personalized coaching insights
#   - Scripture-aware analysis
